'''伊迪斯·波琳·嘉爾特·韋爾遜'''（{{lang-en|Edith Bolling Galt Wilson}}，1872年10月15日－1961年12月28日）是第28任[[美國總統|美國總統]][[伍德羅·威爾遜|伍德羅·威爾遜]]的第二任妻子，在1915年至1921年間擔任[[美國第一夫人|美國第一夫人]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Edith Bolling Galt Wilson|url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/about-the-white-house/first-families/edith-bolling-galt-wilson/|accessdate=2021-01-25|work=白宮|language=en|dead-url=no|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123202736/https://www.whitehouse.gov/about-the-white-house/first-families/edith-bolling-galt-wilson/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=First Lady Biography: Edith Wilson|url=http://www.firstladies.org/biographies/firstladies.aspx?biography=29|accessdate=2010-03-11|publisher=美國國家第一夫人圖書館|dead-url=no|location=俄亥俄州坎頓|archive-date=2012-04-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67AwaschG?url=http://www.firstladies.org/biographies/firstladies.aspx?biography=29}}</ref>。伊迪斯·韋爾遜在1915年12月與[[喪偶|喪偶]]逾一年的伍德羅·威爾遜結婚。

威爾遜任總統期間，伊迪斯一直擔當頗有影響力的角色，甚至在其夫其後於1919年10月多次[[中風|中風]]後的餘下任期間負責管理總統辦公室，並決定哪些信息及國務需要被傳遞予臥床不起的總統威爾遜<ref>William Elliott Hazelgrove, ''Madam President: The Secret Presidency of Edith Wilson'' (Washington, D.C.: Regency Publishing, 2016); Brian Lamb, ''Who's Buried in Grant's Tomb?: A Tour of Presidential Gravesites'' (New York: Public Affairs, 2010), p. 119; Judith L. Weaver, "Edith Bolling, Wilson as First Lady: A Study in the Power of Personality, 1919–1920," ''Presidential Studies Quarterly'' 15, No. 1 (Winter, 1985), pp. 51–76; and Dwight Young and Margaret Johnson, ''Dear First Lady: Letters to the White House: From the Collections of the Library of Congress & National Archives'' (Washington, D.C.: National Geographic, 2008), p. 91.</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=When a secret president ran the country|url=https://www.pbs.org/newshour/health/woodrow-wilson-stroke|date=October 2, 2015|last=Markel|first=Howard|work=PBS NewsHour|publisher=NewsHour Productions|access-date=December 27, 2019|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215190020/https://www.pbs.org/newshour/health/woodrow-wilson-stroke}}</ref>。

